    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to an exacting standard. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within factory tolerances. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to address longitudinal stress fatigue. Power is delivered through a crisp six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension has been upgraded with high-rebound damping coilovers for neutral cornering balance. Finished in pristine original paint with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, and an interior free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination, this vehicle is mechanically and aesthetically flawless.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
