    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defines the term 'mint.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain, let alone snow. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather upholstery still retains its original scent, with no visible wear on the bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, backed by a comprehensive, binder-organized service history from the original dealership. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes both original keys, all manuals, and a custom car cover.",
